title: Requires notaries public to provide evidence of identity for a notarial act and maintain an official journal of notarial acts
summary: Requires notary publics to provide evidence of identity for a notarial act and maintain an official journal of notarial acts.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the executive law, in relation to the duties of notaries public, by requiring evidence of identity for a notarial act and maintenance of an official journal of notarial acts
